ğŸ¨ UI and Styling
    â€¢    Use SwiftUI for all screens. UIKit only if absolutely necessary.
    â€¢    Use SF Symbols for icons and Drawer menu items.
    â€¢    Support Dark Mode and Dynamic Type.
    â€¢    Design with SafeArea and GeometryReader properly.
    â€¢    Avoid hardcoded paddings, use responsive layouts with GeometryProxy.
    â€¢    Use linear/radial gradients sparingly but aesthetically.
    â€¢    Use .sheet, .popover, and NavigationStack for user flow.

